    "_color": {
      "__type__": "cc.Color",
      "r": 0,
      "g": 0,
      "b": 0,
      "a": 255
    },
    "_string": "The core objective of the game is to transmit signals from Earth to incoming spacecraft. Each signal has a specific color, and it must match the color of the target ship. Successfully delivering the correct signal earns you in-game currency, while sending the wrong one results in a penalty.\n\nTo complete your objectives more effectively, you can purchase and place signal reflectors and boosters in available locations. \n\n          - reflectors help redirect signals\n    \n          - boosters increase their range, allowing you to reach more distant ships.",
